  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale input data)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. The model was updated in early 2026 to incorporate revised impeller geometry tolerances; however, the primary rheological dataset used to calibrate blood viscosity and damage accumulation parameters carries a dataVintage from late 2025, predating the model revision. Re-validation against the updated model build is described as planned but has not been completed or documented.",
